---
title: Crispy Pork Tonkatsu with Cucumber Salad and Edamame Rice
description: Tonight we are headed to Japan for a crispy panko-crusted pork cutlet drizzled with Tonkatsu sauce (you can think of it as a soy-based answer to barbecue sauce). And if that’s not enough, the fluffy edamame rice and cucumber salad sides will convince you to make this Japanese comfort food one of your favourites.
